      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Harvest Technologies</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Autologous platelet concentrate will enhance the rate of healing of chronic diabetic wounds
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The treatment of a diabetic wound with APC and thrombinhas the potential to accelerate the
      re-epithial process when compared with usual care. The study is a prospective, randomized,
      blinded, multicenter clinical evaluation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
